WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.376 --> 00:00:05.938
I just want to tell you all that I feel uplifted in my spirit.

00:00:06.236 --> 00:00:14.423
You can just feel the spiritual charge that is taking place in the atmosphere with all these people that are praying.

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:33.629
If one of us can put a thousand to flight and two of us can send 10,000 to flight, think about how many thousands of us sending into flight the power and the authority.

00:00:33.629 --> 00:00:47.376
There is nothing that the Lord can't do through us if we just act in simple faith, believe, pray, and be that army—that body joined together.

00:00:47.376 --> 00:00:57.937
I'm telling you, we are about to see one of the greatest harvests of souls this world has ever seen.

00:00:57.937 --> 00:01:07.548
I want you all to agree with me: take the blinders off of people's eyes.

00:01:15.826 --> 00:01:23.086
A spiritual awakening, a spiritual outpouring of the Spirit of God like we've never seen before—the waking from the slumber of the seeker-friendlies and the people who are asleep spiritually.

00:01:23.086 --> 00:01:37.942
Praying for their eyes to be enlightened, praying for the demonstrations and the manifestations not just to happen in a couple of churches, but in all the churches.

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:42.591
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, it won't just be the Pentecostals, it won't just be the charismatics.

00:01:42.591 --> 00:01:45.693
It will be the body of Christ.

00:01:45.693 --> 00:01:57.613
' It won't be just one denomination—like the Word of Faith bunch that is on fire for the Lord.

00:01:57.613 --> 00:02:19.968
We stand and we know how to live by faith, we know how to live by the Word of God, and we stand on the Word of God, but there are still a lot of people that walk in defeat.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:23.337
I am ready to stop playing church.

00:02:23.337 --> 00:02:35.417
I am tired of going to church and not getting anything—I want that tangible presence of God to the point where you walk away changed.

00:02:35.417 --> 00:02:39.110
I don't want to live where I was five days ago.

00:02:39.110 --> 00:02:45.312
I want to live exceedingly abundantly above all that I dare ask or think.

00:02:45.312 --> 00:02:49.087
People say, 'Well, you had another visit from Jesus?

00:02:49.087 --> 00:02:52.159
' Yes, I expect it.

00:02:52.159 --> 00:02:55.106
I expect Him to show up.

00:02:55.106 --> 00:03:03.733
I expect to have a relationship with the Father; He is my Father.

00:03:09.510 --> 00:03:14.480
It shouldn't be out of the ordinary to have a visitation from the Lord, to have demonstrations and manifestations.

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:29.140
He said greater works would we do.

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:36.189
He said you would lay hands on the sick and they would recover.

00:03:37.369 --> 00:03:45.542
You would cast out devils, bring sight to the blind, and raise the dead.

00:03:56.490 --> 00:03:56.775
He told us we would do this.

00:03:56.775 --> 00:04:04.102
What's amazing, folks, is that's not supposed to be special; that's just the Great Commission.

00:04:04.102 --> 00:04:09.599
He commissioned every single one of us to walk in that authority.

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:11.030
He commissioned every single believer.

00:04:11.030 --> 00:04:13.220
So what does that say?

00:04:13.220 --> 00:04:18.753
A child has the authority to cast out a devil.

00:04:31.055 --> 00:04:31.590
A child has authority to lay hands on the sick and see them recover.

00:04:31.590 --> 00:04:39.194
It didn't say a 'seasoned veteran believer'; he said 'believers,' if you believe.

00:04:39.194 --> 00:04:50.890
So we always feel, 'No, that's for Brother Brandon,' or, 'No, that's for Sister Billy; she's a teacher and God equipped her.

00:04:50.890 --> 00:04:55.394
' No, that's for you, ladies and gentlemen.

00:04:55.394 --> 00:04:57.759
He gave you power.

00:04:57.759 --> 00:05:03.737
He didn't give anybody else special treatment; He is no respecter of persons.

00:05:05.440 --> 00:05:17.302
I want you to be encouraged that you have that ability the moment you accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

00:05:32.130 --> 00:05:32.360
You are seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities, powers, and might.

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:42.515
I'm trying to emphasize how important it is for you to understand who He is and that He lives in you—Christ in you.

00:05:42.515 --> 00:05:50.333
So, I just want to encourage you all today.

00:05:50.333 --> 00:05:56.097
We're going to pray over your situations and your households.

00:05:56.097 --> 00:06:11.240
I'll just pray in the Spirit with you for a little bit and attach my faith with yours for your finances, for an outpouring of finances.

00:06:11.240 --> 00:06:24.337
I'm believing God for cryptos and for big things—gold, silver, and things like that—that God would turn things around and give us witty ideas to get wealth.

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:32.940
God will give you a surplus.

00:06:32.940 --> 00:06:50.384
I'm not just believing for your food to be taken care of today, but for having more than enough to be able to help your neighbor, a loved one, or someone else.

00:06:50.384 --> 00:06:56.503
Believe Him for overflow to take care of other people besides yourself.

00:06:56.503 --> 00:07:00.657
It's time to believe God for big.

00:07:00.657 --> 00:07:10.175
It's time to believe God for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think—to believe Him for the big thing.

00:07:10.175 --> 00:07:15.160
That's where I believe we are: believing God for abundance.

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:17.436
So let's believe Him today.

00:07:21.079 --> 00:07:23.886
Father, we thank you right now in the name of Jesus.

00:07:24.234 --> 00:07:40.159
We speak to the mountain of debt, we speak to the mountain of poverty, and we command it to bow its knee in the name of Jesus and be cast into the sea.

00:07:40.1000 --> 00:07:44.667
Father, I thank you that we have authority over debt and poverty.

00:07:50.187 --> 00:07:50.631
We speak to lack and 'not enough' and barely getting by, and we say: no more.

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:56.274
We have abundance, we have overflow, and we have more than enough in the name of Jesus.

00:07:58.866 --> 00:08:02.590
Thank you, Father, for overflow and for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:08:15.246 --> 00:08:15.680
Thank you, Father, that you've made a way for them not just to live paycheck to paycheck, but to live lavishly.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:21.640
God wants to let you live a great lifestyle, with happiness and abundance.

00:08:21.640 --> 00:08:29.759
Money is not supposed to make us happy, but it's a lot easier to have money than not to have it.

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:38.271
That's what I'm believing for you today: to be able to say you've got enough to help the kingdom of God.

00:08:38.271 --> 00:08:43.572
Father, we thank you and give you praise for it.

00:08:43.572 --> 00:08:49.965
Now we believe for our bodies—that we're whole spiritually, physically, financially, mentally, and emotionally.

00:08:49.965 --> 00:09:04.440
Father, we pray over the bodies, over the health today, that they're healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:09:12.684 --> 00:09:18.086
We speak life over their bodies, from the top of their heads to the soles of their feet.

00:09:23.536 --> 00:09:23.844
Lord, we speak life over their blood and over their cells.

00:09:23.844 --> 00:09:29.265
No cancer, no diabetes, and no heart disease comes nigh them.

00:09:29.265 --> 00:09:39.554
Father, I thank you that you said in your Word that you made them healed by your stripes.

00:09:48.084 --> 00:09:48.395
Thank you, Father, for healing all kinds of infections.

00:09:48.706 --> 00:09:53.288
For somebody, we pray over bladder infections and UTIs right now.

00:09:59.331 --> 00:09:59.903
We speak to it, and in the name of Jesus, the UTI has to go.

00:09:59.903 --> 00:10:04.640
We speak to prostates to be healed and whole in Jesus' name.

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:10.280
Over high blood pressure, we speak in the name of Jesus.

00:10:10.280 --> 00:10:17.703
We thank you, Lord, that you took all those infirmities and bore our sicknesses.

00:10:17.703 --> 00:10:23.737
What you bore in your body, we will not bear in our body.

00:10:23.737 --> 00:10:32.069
I thank you for your healing power that flows on the inside of us.

00:10:32.069 --> 00:10:50.543
Father, I thank you that you put that crown of thorns on for the torment—that you took any kind of mental torment, bad dreams, night terrors, or stress disorders.

00:10:50.543 --> 00:10:55.715
Father, I thank you that they're free from those things.

00:11:12.724 --> 00:11:12.973
You said, 'Whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:11:12.973 --> 00:11:25.400
' It's been on my heart to pray for your finances and for better jobs—for you to be the head, not the tail, and above and not beneath.

00:11:25.400 --> 00:11:31.600
I've been stirred about it because I see so many people who are lacking.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:37.794
It's time to turn it around and believe God for big.

00:11:37.794 --> 00:11:49.649
Instead of saying, 'I have enough for some ramen noodles and Beanie Weenies to get me through the week,' you should be the King's kid eating salmon filets.

00:11:49.649 --> 00:12:03.256
There is nothing wrong with eating ramen noodles, but I'm believing God for overflow so you can say, 'Lord, thank you that the world has our stuff.

00:12:03.256 --> 00:12:10.760
' We're tithers, givers, and sowers, and the wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:12:13.826 --> 00:12:19.795
The Lord has me praying about the wealth of the sinner's hand being laid up for the just.

00:12:19.795 --> 00:12:24.768
The devil's crowd has it, but we're the King's kids.

00:12:26.138 --> 00:12:32.800
He has the cattle on a thousand hills and overflow in the name of Jesus.

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:38.556
As He is, so are we in this world—on earth as it is in heaven.

00:12:38.556 --> 00:12:53.300
Because we are flowing in that covenant with Him, I'm going to tell you: if you have a problem with prosperity and walking in the blessing, you're going to hate heaven.

00:12:54.726 --> 00:13:03.547
From what I've seen, even Jesus' crown and the jewels—it's beyond anything you can dare ask or think.

00:13:06.868 --> 00:13:07.199
The mansions in heaven are overflow.

00:13:07.199 --> 00:13:13.416
There's no poverty in heaven, no trailer parks, and no shacks.

00:13:13.416 --> 00:13:18.256
There are mansions and castles; I've seen them, and they're breathtaking.

00:13:18.256 --> 00:13:22.029
The gold is transparent in the streets.

00:13:22.029 --> 00:13:29.331
Like Dorothy in The Wizard of Oz, follow the Yellow Brick Road.

00:13:29.331 --> 00:13:32.399
This is transparent gold; it's so pure and beautiful.

00:13:32.399 --> 00:13:42.140
If you just took out one brick of that street, most people could live forever off it because of how pure that gold is.

00:13:47.057 --> 00:13:52.199
I know this is probably getting on some people's nerves, but the Lord wants you blessed.

00:13:52.199 --> 00:14:03.937
I feel it inside to tell you today that God wants you to have exceedingly abundantly above all you dare ask or think.

00:14:03.937 --> 00:14:15.486
To the tithers and givers who have sowed and sowed and never reaped: it's a spiritual law for seed-time and harvest.

00:14:18.649 --> 00:14:22.199
A lot of you believe in sowing, but you don't believe in reaping.

00:14:26.053 --> 00:14:30.720
You push away the reaping because it's uncomfortable or you feel you should just be humble.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
God will build the character in you so money won't destroy you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
He's a God of love.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I hope this video blessed you all today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Stop thinking small and believe God bigger.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
He is a big God, and if the devil's crowd can have it, we should take it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
It's time to plunder hell and populate heaven and take authority over the devil.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
He gave you dominion.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
Whatsoever things you bind on earth will be bound in heaven, and whatsoever things you loose on earth will be loosed in heaven.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
He said whatsoever things *you* say out of your mouth and believe in your heart will come to pass.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Expectation brings manifestation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I thank you, Father, that it's coming to pass.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
The seeds we sowed in the past will come to harvest at last in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Amen and amen and amen.
